name: Founder Card 00016
description:
how to describe la creme de la creme?
first of all is an imaginary place in my mind where anything can happens that was turned into the genesis piece of the collection that has the same name and after that into a weird, nasty & fancy meta verse club.
to add more fun I decided to test how a DAO works and some decisions about the collection such as places, characters on artworks, size or pricing on some eds will be taken my DAO founders.
DAO members in first instance are the primary buyers of the genesis piece but with time this can change.
this account will handle the DAO profit and some mints.
this is the first DAO member Founder card.

let's have some fun
